high_descs: Head towards the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the black cup near the backsplash.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the black cup on the top shelf. Close the refrigerator door for seven seconds. Open the fridge door. Take out the cup. Close the fridge door.
Turn left and take the cup to the small black table in the corner.
Put the cup on the black table to the left of the watermelon.
anns.task_desc: Put the black cup in the fridge for seven seconds, put it on small black table.

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the cup on the bottom shelf of the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and take the cup out.
Walk left to the corner where the black table is.
Place the cup on the black table to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup on a table.

high_descs: Move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the black cup from the counter.
Bring the cup to the fridge.
Chill the cup in the fridge.
Bring the cup to the small black table.
Put the cup on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup on the small black table.
